<subSubSection id="B5B222A4871259AF96BC70A52B6CC539" pageId="0" pageNumber="81" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph id="915257261165259D92BA05998BF78D31" pageId="0" pageNumber="81">Diagnosis.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="9459435319C9EFC4BC6C7B124D29F9BD" pageId="0" pageNumber="81">
Differing from subsp. 
<taxonomicName id="116A605DD82A3A56B6F0735DFA4CAD2C" authority="leichtlinii" class="Liliopsida" family="Liliaceae" genus="Lilium" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Lilium leichtlinii subsp. leichtlinii" order="Liliales" pageId="0" pageNumber="81" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="subSpecies" species="leichtlinii" subSpecies="leichtlinii">Lilium leichtlinii leichtlinii</taxonomicName>
in the following characters: 
<emphasis id="516520DA5A2A00E0628F316714DB6107" bold="true" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="81">bulb</emphasis>
with stolons that can extend to 
<quantity id="0C0BB7C0FE2514C623BB8B8EFBBCB24F" metricMagnitude="0" metricUnit="m" metricValue="2.0" unit="m" value="2.0">2 m</quantity>
; 
<emphasis id="0D0544563FB67CAF822533DD96E5EBF5" bold="true" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="81">stem</emphasis>
green, purple streaked or spotted (vs. stem green unspotted); 
<emphasis id="8C0817F82AA76B403BA4BC14FDF8B0B9" bold="true" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="81">leaves</emphasis>
linear or lanceolate to 
<quantity id="AB0FF8833AD2B0B175314292CEBE3C36" metricMagnitude="-2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.6" unit="cm" value="1.6">1.6 cm</quantity>
wide (vs. 
<quantity id="35ABE6FEE6B7072DB3A896830B3A0759" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="8.5" metricValueMax="12.0" metricValueMin="5.0" unit="cm" value="0.85" valueMax="1.2" valueMin="0.5">0.5-1.2 cm</quantity>
wide); 
<emphasis id="A304153D685A908258D09573BCB245DF" bold="true" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="81">Inflorescence</emphasis>
with (2) -5-12 flowers, 
<emphasis id="7DDFDA5BD4587E81F4C2C90A17443707" bold="true" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="81">flowers</emphasis>
light orange or reddish-orange with dark reddish-brown speckling, rarely reddish-brown streaking (vs. yellow), nectaries with orange-red papillae marginally (vs. yellow); stamens with pale orange filaments (vs. pale yellow), anthers brown, pollen reddish-orange (vs. yellowish-brown); 
<emphasis id="E230084ACD274D3D1AAF2A52195976F6" bold="true" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="81">style</emphasis>
pale orange (vs. pale yellow).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
